Package: MaxContrastProjection
Type: Package
Title: Perform a maximum contrast projection of 3D images along the z-dimension into 2D
Version: 0.99.1
Date: 2017-02-08
Author: Jan Sauer, Bernd Fischer
Maintainer: Jan Sauer <jan.sauer@dkfz-heidelberg.de>
Description: This R/Bioconductor package provides methods to project 3D images
    stacks along the z-dimension to 2D. Different methods like maximum intensity 
    projection and maximal contrast projection are implemented.
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyLoad: true
Imports:
    EBImage, stats
Depends:
    methods, R (>= 3.4)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    knitr, BiocStyle
SystemRequirements: GNU make
biocViews: Software, Visualization
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
